flavor_text_entries.gold:
It always stands
on one foot. It
changes feet so fast, the movement
can rarely be
seen.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
It has a perfect
sense of time.
Whatever happens, it keeps rhythm by
precisely tilting
its head in time.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
It begins to hoot
at the same time
every day. Some trainers use them
in place of
clocks.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
HOOTHOOT has an internal organ that
senses and tracks the earth’s rotation.
Using this special organ, this POKéMON begins hooting at precisely the same
time every day.
